---
title: Crispy Falafel on Spiced Pilaf with Tomato-Cucumber Salad and Raita
description: Crispy falafel sit atop an aromatic pilaf delicately flavoured with Mediterranean spices and naturally sweetened with raisins. The tomato-cucumber side salad adds a refreshing bite and a cooling cucumber raita is the perfect dipper!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/falafels-croustillants-sur-pilaf-aux-epices-c9faa00d.jpg
